readme:
# atom-monokai theme

Atom syntax theme inspired by [monokai](http://www.monokai.nl/blog/2006/07/15/textmate-color-theme/).
Works with Atom Dark, Light and Seti UI.

![](https://raw.github.com/burntime/atom-monokai/master/screenshot.png)
